product_name: Fred Perry Classic Shoulder Bag Ox Blood
description: Fred Perry Classic Shoulder Bag Ox Blood  Colourway; Ox Blood, Grey  This classic shoulder bag is inspired by messenger style bags, crafted in ox blood PVC. The top and side sections of the bag are grey PVC. There is a flat pocket to the front of the bag which has grey cotton trim and there is also a zipped inner pocket. The bag fastens by a zip accross the top of the bag's body and the adjustable shoulder strap is in ox blood and grey. The iconic Laurel wreath logo is in gold to the front side of the bag, completing the classic vintage feel.
